- I was waiting for you.

33
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:32,090
You've never had an archery lesson since you've joined the team, right?

34
00:03:32,090 --> 00:03:34,430
I see you do it all the time.

35
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:37,190
It's so easy! Just like this.

36
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:39,460
You're so arrogant.

37
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:42,390
Archery is not as easy as it seems.

38
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:46,240
How about this? Let me teach you since I have nothing to do today.

39
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:48,609
Just come here.

40
00:03:48,609 --> 00:03:51,410
Come! Stand like this.

41
00:03:51,410 --> 00:03:55,219
Come! Feet shoulder width apart, face your right.

42
00:03:55,219 --> 00:03:57,739
Come! I've loaded the arrow for you.

43
00:03:57,740 --> 00:04:01,509
Hold the bow between the thumb

44
00:04:01,509 --> 00:04:03,840
and index finger. Right!

45
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,990
I'll set up the clicker.

46
00:04:05,990 --> 00:04:08,579
Like this! Yes, very good.

47
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:10,579
- Like this?
- Great! You're talented.

48
00:04:10,579 --> 00:04:12,909
- I can't lift it.
- Here! Let me help you.

49
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:15,810
Here! Here! Pull.

50
00:04:15,810 --> 00:04:18,570
Aim! Count down, okay?

51
00:04:18,570 --> 00:04:21,229
Three. Two. One.

52
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:22,930
Release!

53
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:25,539
Ten points!

54
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:27,950
I'm a genius.

55
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:30,820
You're amazing!

56
00:04:38,090 --> 00:04:42,160
Do you mind if I marry into your family?

57
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,950
I mean

58
