You don't?

64
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:22,460
Nie Yue, will you marry me?

65
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:26,050
Yes, I will.

66
00:05:46,850 --> 00:05:49,640
Fang Fang, I'm back.

67
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:52,640
Did you miss me?

68
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:09,210
Fang Fang, what do you think is inside this little black box?

69
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,670
I can't hear a thing inside.

70
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:20,950
It's quite heavy, too.

71
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:25,390
I wonder what's inside.

72
00:06:25,910 --> 00:06:27,610
Fang Fang.

73
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:31,210
I can tell you've already eaten.

74
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:35,450
What is this? Help me open it!

75
00:06:37,110 --> 00:06:39,140
Your brother is calling.

76
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,189
Why are you back so early?

77
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:45,300
They didn't send you home?

78
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:48,260
No, I had dinner with my friend today.

79
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:51,230
I told them not to send me.

80
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:53,330
Were you with a boy or a girl?

81
00:06:53,330 --> 00:06:55,530
I'm not telling you.

82
00:06:55,530 --> 00:06:56,739
Ye Shaowen?

83
00:06:56,740 --> 00:06:59,230
How can that be possible?

84
00:06:59,230 --> 00:07:05,290
I told you before that I'm a female swan.

85
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:08,800
Swans are monogamous, right?

86
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:13,790
Anyway, the male swan is coming back next week.

87
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:17,460
Really?

88
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:21,020
Are you serious?

89
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:24,090
Hold on! I'll get Fang Fang to dance for you.

90
00:07:24,090 --> 00:07:28,739
Fang Fang, your brother's coming back, are you happy?

91
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:30,739
Come! Dance for your brother.

92
00:07:30,740 --> 00:07:34,529
Stand! One. Two.

93
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:38,850
Isn't he good at dancing?

94
00:07:38,850 --> 00:07:41,290
Your brother is coming back.

95
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:49,539
Was the operation for the dog successful?

96
00:07:49,540 --> 00:07:51,539
It was very successful, the dog was very obedient.

97
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:53,220
That's good.

98
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:55,969
- Can you open it for me?
- All right.

99
00:07:55,969 --> 00:07:58,170
Thank you.

100
00:07:58,970 --> 00:08:01,360
My boyfriend will come back in a few days.

101
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:05,259
Boyfriend? You rented one?

102
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:07,040
You're the one who rented one.

103
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:10,190
Aren't you single?

104
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,909
Where is he from?

105
