127
00:10:00,210 --> 00:10:02,970
Fang Fang, it's been a while.

128
00:10:02,970 --> 00:10:05,610
Have you missed me?

129
00:10:06,050 --> 00:10:10,359
You gained weight, she took good care of you.

130
00:10:10,359 --> 00:10:14,229
I would have cleaned the house if I knew you were coming back. It's so messy!

131
00:10:20,730 --> 00:10:22,660
How's my new house?

132
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:29,640
It's not bad! It's way better than the old kennel.

133
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:32,170
It'll become a real kennel now that you're back.

134
00:10:38,690 --> 00:10:43,260
I think you look... slightly better under the light.

135
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,930
Slightly?

136
00:10:45,690 --> 00:10:47,640
Don't be greedy!

137
00:10:50,170 --> 00:10:54,410
Will you still go abroad after this?

138
00:10:55,610 --> 00:10:59,100
No! Rehabilitation training is done.

139
00:10:59,100 --> 00:11:01,550
- Really?
- Really.

140
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:04,869
That's great! Our family has been reunited.

141
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:08,090
Look at me!

142
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:15,550
So, you are looking at that thing?

143
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:19,240
It's been with me for so long.

144
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,180
What's the password?

145
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:23,370
I tried so many different one's but I could never figure it out.

146
00:11:23,370 --> 00:11:25,300
Take a guess!

147
00:11:25,300 --> 00:11:27,830
Don't tell me you forgot the password.

148
00:11:27,830 --> 00:11:31,490
Now that you mention it, I don't think I remember it.

149
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:34,480
How dare you! It's only four numbers anyway.

150
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,670
Only ten thousand combinations for me to try.

151
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:38,650
Give it to me!

152
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,460
Go and take a shower.

153
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:53,560
I just got here, let me rest for a while.

154
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:58,530
- You reek of sweat. Go now!
- I don't reek of sweat.

155
00:11:58,530 --> 00:12:01,359
Yes, you do! I can smell it. Quickly!

156
00:12:01,359 --> 00:12:03,560
Don't scare Fang Fang!

157
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:24,120
What are you looking at? Turn around!

158
00:12:27,370 --> 00:12:29,170
Aren't you ashamed of yourself?

159
00:12:57,300 --> 00:12:59,100
Chi-chi!

160
00:13:04,810 --> 00:13:06,410
Chi-chi.

161
00:13:34,030 --> 00:13:36,230
What are you doing?

162
00:13:36,230 --> 00:13:37,750
Going to sleep!

163
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:39,950
You're not sleeping on the bed?

164
00:13:40,860 --> 00:13:44,479
Just sleep! Don't you have work tomorrow?

165
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:54,010
Oh, no! I have an evaluation exam today.

166
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:57,800
Oh, no! I'm done for, I'm going to be late.

167
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:59,900
Why didn't you wake me earlier?

168
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:05,320
By the way, I'm going to go see Coach Liu this afternoon.

169
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:08,280
I'll go find you when I'm done with training.

170
00:15:08,289 --> 00:15:09,620
All right.

171
00:15:14,570 --> 00:15:16,530
Fang Fang, good morning!

172
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:22,970
- I'm leaving.
- Be careful!

173
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:45,760
This again?

174
00:15:52,830 --> 00:15:57,110
Fang Fang, let me clean up the table.

175
00:15:57,110 --> 00:16:00,020
Isn't it messy?

176
00:16:10,950 --> 00:16:16,500
June 20th. Clear. Xu Fang left today.

177
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:20,099
My most important wish for the upcoming days

178
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:22,940
is to successfully find work

179
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:25,440
so Fang Fang won't have to worry.

180
00:16:26,610 --> 00:16:32,080
July 31st. Cloudy. I've worked at the hospital for some time now,

181
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:37,120
but no one believed me when I told them I have a boyfriend.

182
00:16:38,220 --> 00:16:41,510
August 15th. Clear.

183
00:16:42,590 --> 00:16:45,050
I miss everyone.

184
00:16:45,050 --> 00:16:49,069
I miss the times when I ate at the stalls outside the university

185
00:16:49,070 --> 00:16:51,410
with Nie Yue.

186
00:16:51,410 --> 00:16:55,240
I wonder how they are now.

187
00:16:57,300 --> 00:17:00,140
September 1st. Clear.

188
00:17:00,140 --> 00:17:01,930
Watching a movie alone.

189
00:17:01,930 --> 00:17:03,650
Eating alone.

190
00:17:03,650 --> 00:17:06,030
Sleeping alone.

191
00:17:06,039 --> 00:17:09,910
But I have someone inside my heart.

192
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:42,720
Straighten the arrow. Keep it straight. That's wrong!

193
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:47,220
Lower your shoulder! Is that how I taught you?

194
00:17:47,220 --> 00:17:49,999
Coach, I feel more comfortable like this.

195
00:17:49,999 --> 00:17:53,400
I heard our university's sharpshooter shoots like this.

196
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:58,280
Master the basics before you try to learn someone else's method.

197
00:17:58,280 --> 00:18:02,540
I would call you my mentor if you hit the gold ring every time.

198
00:18:04,230 --> 00:18:06,300
Straighten your arrow!

199
00:18:12,850 --> 00:18:14,560
Xu Fang?

200
00:18:17,620 --> 00:18:19,120
Come here!

201
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,860
When did you come back?

202
00:18:21,860 --> 00:18:24,190
Just last night.

203
00:18:24,190 --> 00:18:27,139
You brat! Can't you give me a call?

204
00:18:27,140 --> 00:18:29,600
I didn't have the time.

205
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:31,990
I've been waiting for this day for so long.

206
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:38,529
Come here! Let me introduce you to my new team members.

207
00:18:38,529 --> 00:18:42,300
Stop for a while, come here! Come here!

208
00:18:46,710 --> 00:18:48,810
Do you all know who this is?

209
00:18:50,660 --> 00:18:54,359
The famous athlete from our university, Xu Fang.

210
00:18:54,359 --> 00:18:56,150
Xu Fang?

211
00:18:56,150 --> 00:18:58,270
The national champion?

212
00:18:58,270 --> 00:19:01,020
Senior Xu Fang, show us some shots.

213
00:19:01,950 --> 00:19:05,289
Forget about it! He just came back from rehabilitation training.

214
00:19:05,289 --> 00:19:09,600
It's tiring and he needs rest, he will show you another day.

215
00:19:09,600 --> 00:19:11,740
All right.

216
00:19:11,740 --> 00:19:14,539
See! This is your goal.

217
00:19:14,539 --> 00:19:17,870
Your future is in your hands! Are you all confident?

218
00:19:17,870 --> 00:19:19,630
Yes!

219
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:21,190
Keep training.

220
00:19:26,870 --> 00:19:28,470
Thank you, Coach.

221
00:19:28,470 --> 00:19:34,100
What for? They idolize you; make sure to act mysterious.

222
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:36,150
Xu Fang.

223
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:42,800
The next competition will be a real challenge against yourself.

224
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:46,920
That version of yourself is the true Xu Fang.

225
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,800
Hello. I...

226
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:24,990
Is there anything I can help you with?

227
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:29,219
I'm sorry! We were just playing around.

228
00:20:29,219 --> 00:20:31,020
- I'll take him back.
- That's okay.

229
00:20:31,020 --> 00:20:33,020
I'm looking for Doctor Lin Xichi.

230
00:20:33,020 --> 00:20:35,270
Do you have an appointment?

231
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:37,430
I'm her boyfriend.

232
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:43,199
The legendary boyfriend! I finally get to meet you today.

233
00:20:43,199 --> 00:20:46,589
I'll call her. So handsome!

234
00:20:57,600 --> 00:21:00,220
- What do you want to eat?
- What do you want to eat?

235
00:21:00,220 --> 00:21:02,290
Anything.

236
00:21:02,290 --> 00:21:04,270
Follow me then!

237
00:21:04,990 --> 00:21:07,570
You have had a plan all along, why asked me?

238
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:14,379
Did you do that on purpose? You could've just called me.

239
00:21:14,379 --> 00:21:18,520
How would your colleagues know that your boyfriend isn't imaginary then?

240
00:21:19,439 --> 00:21:21,840
Xu Fang, did you read my diary?

241
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:23,270
- It hurts!
- Tell me! Did you read it?

242
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:26,469
It hurts! Hold on. Hold on. Stop.

243
00:21:27,300 --> 00:21:31,299
It was meant for you to write your wishes to me, why couldn't I read it?

244
00:21:31,299 --> 00:21:36,250
And from now on, I'll fulfill every wish for you.

245
00:21:36,950 --> 00:21:39,800
Let's take a plane ride!

246
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:05,789
Take off!

247
00:22:14,380 --> 00:22:16,210
It's so lively here now. There are so many snack shops.

248
00:22:16,210 --> 00:22:18,080
There are so many snack shops.

249
00:22:18,089 --> 00:22:20,640
Do you want to try them all?

250
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:24,590
My dream is to eat everything in the world.

251
00:22:24,590 --> 00:22:29,470
Sure! Let's eat everything here for today.

252
00:22:29,470 --> 00:22:31,020
Look!

253
00:22:34,300 --> 00:22:36,930
- Is that Nie Yue?
- I think so.

254
00:22:36,930 --> 00:22:39,970
Jiang Zhengxu and Xin Zidan are beside her.

255
00:22:39,970 --> 00:22:41,570
Nie Yue!

256
00:22:46,330 --> 00:22:48,660
- Brother Chi.
- Brother Chi.

257
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:52,319
Why is everyone here? Everyone's here.

258
00:22:58,020 --> 00:23:01,049
- I missed you.
- I missed all of you.

259
00:23:01,049 --> 00:23:02,290
How is everyone?

260
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:04,229
- We're good.
- Everyone's good.

261
00:23:04,229 --> 00:23:07,490
Everyone's good. Not bad!

262
00:23:10,260 --> 00:23:13,719
- You two got married?
- No! We got engaged.

263
00:23:13,719 --> 00:23:16,820
We'll get married later.

264
00:23:16,820 --> 00:23:21,130
You got engaged without telling me? I can cheer for both of you.

265
00:23:21,130 --> 00:23:24,969
Well, Xu Fang isn't here, you might be sad if you saw.

266
00:23:24,969 --> 00:23:27,180
Won't you be jealous?

267
00:23:27,180 --> 00:23:31,580
That's enough! Since you didn't call me,

268
00:23:31,580 --> 00:23:34,250
this meal is on you.

269
00:23:34,250 --> 00:23:37,469
This meal doesn't count! You promised to pay.

270
00:23:37,469 --> 00:23:38,620
- That's right.
- That's right.

271
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:41,700
Me? Why?

272
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:45,710
Xu Fang said you'd treat us.

273
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:50,650
You're here?

274
00:23:50,650 --> 00:23:55,779
It's because of someone's wish to eat with everyone at the stalls near the university.

275
00:23:55,779 --> 00:23:57,350
Right?

276
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:01,100
I'll pay.

277
00:24:01,100 --> 00:24:02,770
All right! Sit down.

278
00:24:02,770 --> 00:24:06,160
It's a simple wish, we can fulfill it for you.

279
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:08,800
When will you two get married?

280
00:24:08,800 --> 00:24:10,780
We are not in a rush.

281
00:24:13,490 --> 00:24:17,159
Brother, just endure it! Women are like that.

282
00:24:18,260 --> 00:24:20,589
- Why did you hit me?
- What are you talking about?

283
00:24:20,590 --> 00:24:24,859
Chi-chi waited for Xu Fang for so long, she can't wait until he retires.

284
00:24:24,859 --> 00:24:28,659
You'll have to leave for competitions often if you become professional.

285
00:24:28,660 --> 00:24:32,000
You two will often be separated.

286
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:38,990
It will be like last time when you couldn't take care of Chi-chi or if there's an emergency.

287
00:24:40,170 --> 00:24:42,509
- Let's not talk about that today.
- Yes, let's not.

288
00:24:42,509 --> 00:24:44,779
This is a reception party for Xu Fang.

289
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:46,489
- Come! Come!
- Bottoms up!

290
00:24:46,489 --> 00:24:47,269
- Cheers, Xu Fang!
- Bottoms up!

291
00:24:47,269 --> 00:24:50,860
You can't use that, use this!

292
00:24:50,860 --> 00:24:53,190
- Everyone is using the can?
- You can really drink.

293
00:24:53,190 --> 00:24:55,100
Come! I'm using the can too.

294
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:58,169
- Cheers!
- Cheers.

295
00:24:58,169 --> 00:25:01,000
Drink more! Lin Xichi is paying today.

296
00:25:06,750 --> 00:25:10,570
Didn't you have a wish to reserve a hall and watch movies with me?

297
00:25:10,570 --> 00:25:13,290
There's no one here.

298
00:25:13,290 --> 00:25:15,240
- It's the whole hall.
- Good!

299
00:25:21,980 --> 00:25:24,190
No one's here.

300
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:30,190
Then can we...

301
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:45,040
What are you doing?

302
00:25:45,900 --> 00:25:49,109
I mean you can take off your shoes and put your feet up.

303
00:25:49,110 --> 00:25:52,310
There's no one here! It's starting.

304
00:26:48,420 --> 00:26:50,379
- Look at your little hand!
- Look at yourself!

305
00:26:50,379 --> 00:26:53,200
Holding your hand is like holding a dog's paw.

306
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:55,220
You're the dog.

307
00:26:57,350 --> 00:26:59,650
What do you want to eat today?

308
00:26:59,650 --> 00:27:02,710
Time flies when I'm with you.

309
00:27:02,710 --> 00:27:04,940
I need to think about what to eat every day.

310
00:27:04,949 --> 00:27:07,150
Meal by meal.

311
00:27:07,150 --> 00:27:12,369
People say you're set for life once you marry a man but it's still early for you.

312
00:27:14,170 --> 00:27:18,090
Jiang Zhengxu and Nie Yue are already engaged.

313
00:27:20,230 --> 00:27:23,070
They might get married soon.

314
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,490
You're right.

315
00:27:29,690 --> 00:27:31,290
Tired?

316
00:27:31,290 --> 00:27:34,160
Yes, just a bit.

317
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:38,000
Why don't we take a break at the Civil Affairs Bureau up ahead?

318
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:41,220
They have benches and vending machines.

319
00:27:42,380 --> 00:27:45,250
Let's not go there, we'll be home soon.

320
00:27:48,590 --> 00:27:50,840
When do you plan to marry me?

321
00:27:52,710 --> 00:27:54,340
What?

322
00:27:55,280 --> 00:27:56,419
No, that's not like that, right.

323
00:27:56,420 --> 00:28:01,910
You're still a young and beautiful lady, and your future is bright ahead of you.

324
00:28:03,900 --> 00:28:06,430
What do you mean?

325
00:28:06,430 --> 00:28:08,500
State it clearly!

326
00:28:11,210 --> 00:28:15,030
It's so embarrassing for you to propose to me in the public. Let's go!

327
00:28:19,520 --> 00:28:21,590
How could you?

328
00:28:22,230 --> 00:28:26,059
We've known each other for most of our lives and we've dated for so long.

329
00:28:26,059 --> 00:28:28,480
I've waited for more than a year.

330
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:32,580
Now, you are saying that I'm proposing to you?

331
00:28:32,580 --> 00:28:34,420
Am I wrong?

332
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:42,400
You're really angry?

333
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:47,239
All right, all right! It's my fault.

334
00:28:47,239 --> 00:28:51,149
Don't be angry! Don't cry.

335
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,470
So your agreeing?

336
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:57,450
I'll consider it.

337
00:28:59,470 --> 00:29:01,290
My efforts were wasted.

338
00:29:02,390 --> 00:29:06,209
The supermarket is just in front, I'll cook you anything you want to eat today.

339
00:29:06,209 --> 00:29:07,570
I'm not eating anything.

340
00:29:07,570 --> 00:29:10,590
I'll cook everything myself, how's that?

341
00:29:10,590 --> 00:29:13,110
This is a once in a lifetime chance.

342
00:29:13,110 --> 00:29:16,120
You only care about eating.

343
00:29:22,470 --> 00:29:24,270
Let me do it!

344
00:29:24,270 --> 00:29:29,079
It's not your job! Your job is to hug me.

345
00:29:42,230 --> 00:29:44,850
You're so good at cooking.

346
00:29:44,850 --> 00:29:47,990
I won't eat takeout ever again.

347
00:29:48,800 --> 00:29:53,540
Why don't you cook while I get the ingredients for tomorrow?

348
00:29:54,260 --> 00:29:56,590
I'm going to Beijing tomorrow.

349
00:30:00,470 --> 00:30:02,350
Do you have to go?

350
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:04,760
Here is the thing.

351
00:30:04,760 --> 00:30:07,480
The National Championships are coming up.

352
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:10,910
Coach Liu got me an entry to the competition.

353
00:30:11,930 --> 00:30:16,540
I'll get the chance to join the national team if I perform well.

354
00:30:25,710 --> 00:30:29,350
Is it alright for you to join a competition?

355
00:30:33,570 --> 00:30:36,450
I know you came back from your training abroad.

356
00:30:36,450 --> 00:30:38,220
You must be confident.

357
00:30:38,220 --> 00:30:39,970
But...

358
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:43,990
I don't know what will happen, either.

359
00:30:44,710 --> 00:30:47,200
But I have to go.

360
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:52,230
So I will know the results of my year-long training.

361
00:32:03,970 --> 00:32:06,380
Fang Fang, I'm leaving.

362
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:08,990
Take care of your sister, understand?

363
00:32:16,950 --> 00:32:18,590
Bye-bye.

