[2nd Venue]

365
00:33:18,470 --> 00:33:21,950
Xu Fang, after we were separated,

366
00:33:21,950 --> 00:33:25,070
I feel that I've grown up.

367
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:27,520
Growing up means

368
00:33:27,520 --> 00:33:32,120
not feeling sad about being all alone,

369
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:37,110
because there's something immovable in my heart.

