00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:48,100
[Xu Fang]

376
00:35:24,780 --> 00:35:26,460
Be careful!

377
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:28,470
Feeling better?

378
00:35:28,470 --> 00:35:30,270
Much better.

379
00:35:34,440 --> 00:35:35,990
Why are you here?

380
00:35:35,990 --> 00:35:39,299
She insisted because she missed it the last time, she won't miss it again.

381
00:35:39,299 --> 00:35:41,099
It'll be hard to watch Brother Fang's match again.

382
00:35:41,100 --> 00:35:44,959
If he does join the national team, he'll have to go abroad.

383
00:35:44,959 --> 00:35:46,749
Take good care of her!

384
00:35:46,750 --> 00:35:48,059
You are wrong.

385
00:35:48,060 --> 00:35:49,619
She has screws in her legs now.

386
00:35:49,620 --> 00:35:52,610
It's an awesome mechanical leg.

387
00:35:52,610 --> 00:35:56,049
Be careful! Relax, relax!

388
00:35:57,680 --> 00:35:59,550
Where is Xu Fang?

389
00:36:17,380 --> 00:36:20,919
- Can you slow down and wait for me?
- Hurry up!

390
00:36:20,919 --> 00:36:24,419
We almost missed the plane because of you and you're still dallying.

391
00:36:24,420 --> 00:36:28,149
- You won't become successful.
- Your bag is too heavy.

392
00:36:29,650 --> 00:36:33,330
Why did we end up running instead of taking a taxi this morning?

393
00:36:33,330 --> 00:36:37,440
- It's not expensive.
- We are trying to be thrifty.

394
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:39,430
All right, be thrifty!

